[{"type":"text","level":0,"children":[{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"忘记了是什么原因而欠下了礼物，但还记得礼物的内容——每走过一个城市便送你一份关于这个城市的东西。算起来这个礼物已经拖了大概5年了。随着时间的推移，走的城市越来越多，债也越欠越大，原计划的礼物中有三个城市，现在如果如约完成，估计得有20+了。所以，我就自作主张的把这份礼物缩减为3个城市，希望你不要介意。"}]},{"type":"text","level":0},{"type":"text","level":0,"children":[{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"关于上海的内容其实很早就已经动笔了，最初是在1"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"９"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"年一个深秋的午后，当时我的上一家公司濒临倒闭，员工也裁的七七八八，我也是其中的一员。在全家随便解决了午餐之后，晒着橙黄色的、微冷的阳光，我掏出本子，写下了题目《三个上海》。后来本子不知道被我扔到了哪里，内容也记不起来了，只剩下了这个名字。有趣的是，我从第一次到上海，到今日离开上海，刚好三次，倒是和这个题目合上了。"}]},{"type":"text","level":0},{"type":"text","level":0,"children":[{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"第一次到上海是17年毕业，在无锡的公司草草培训一个多月，便开始了在上海为期三个月的出差。怀着紧张和兴奋下了火车，还没来得及感受大城市的繁华，便被地铁售票机前十几个人的长队震了一下。当时已经是夜里10点多了，这里却拥挤异常，不见任何停歇的痕迹，这便是魔都留给我的第一面。"}]},{"type":"text","level":0},{"type":"text","level":0,"children":[{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"刚到上海的一切都很新鲜，第一次见到全家，第一次去星巴克，第一次看到穿楼越野的地铁。但工作的日子也很无聊，每天挤着早高峰，吃着味道规范的包子，在几十层的写字楼里等电梯，在十几人的会议室里听需求，中午全家或者外卖，下午的咖啡，晚上则大多是小笼包或者葱油面。日子、工作、食物，他们以同样的面貌重复着，重复着。上海如同一个延时纪录片一般，人们匆匆挤上地铁，匆匆吃过午饭，匆匆挤地铁回家，高效的有些搞笑。那时的上海如果晴，就晴的刺眼，高楼耸枳，晃晃的反射着阳光，如果阴，就阴个彻底，然后迅速下起暴雨，噼里啪啦的击打着写字楼的玻璃。上海如同威严的巨人，高大，壮观，迅速，没有任何儿女情长。虽然那时候我并没有一个魔都打工人的自觉，但现在想来，那样的生活就是上海打工人真实的样子了。"}]},{"type":"text","level":0},{"type":"text","level":0,"children":[{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"有时候下班早了，还会出去跑一跑步。"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"我"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"也因此"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"看到了上海不对我敞开的一面。弄堂取代了写字楼，梧桐树遮蔽了路灯，小路上走的多是行人而非车辆。"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"不宽的"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"小路旁"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，精致的店面里"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，陈列的是一辆辆豪车"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"。"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"穿着"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"居家服"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"下楼散步的男女，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"说笑着"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"走进"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"了酒吧"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"十里洋场"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"就这么翻开了一个书角"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"。"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"这也是魔都。"}]},{"type":"text","level":0},{"type":"text","level":0,"children":[{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"三个月"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"的时光"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"是匆匆地，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"带着刚工作的兴奋劲儿，初见上海的好奇劲儿，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"我结束了这与上海的第一次"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"相见。"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"现在回想起来，只记"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"闷热的天，高大的楼"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，小资的街道和行人了。"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"有一件事倒是值得一提，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"上海出差结束之后，便去了北京继续出差，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"落地北京的时候，已经是１１月左右了。站在朝阳的"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"街头"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"看着萧瑟的落叶"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，吸着干爽的"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"冷气，忽然意识到我回到北方了，虽不是东北，但也"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"涌上了"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"熟悉的感觉，闭上眼，甚至能感受到独属于北方的味道。"}]},{"type":"text","level":0},{"type":"text","level":0,"children":[{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"再次回到"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"上海大概是"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"１"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"９"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"年初的样子，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"从"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"北京的公司裸辞之后，就一个人跑到上海"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"找工作了。"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"至于为什么跑这么远"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，也不过是因为有一个面试"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"的邀请，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"刚毕业的日子里就是这样，一个人"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，三两箱行李，东奔西走"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"。"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"找工作的过程是有趣的，每天坐着地铁穿梭在上海的各地，吃饭"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"大概就是全家的三明治，看着地铁里"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"各自"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"忙着的行人，走在不同的街道，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"自得其乐。"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"最后我"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"找到了一份在"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"闵行"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"附近的工作，附近租了个"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"隔断房，每天骑着我的小自行车上下班，工作也不算忙碌，下班之后仍有时间可以去健身。那段时间最大的乐趣就是走在闵行"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"的老居民区，吃一吃街边的小面馆，或"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"是健身之后顺路买一份猪头肉"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"。也是"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"那时，我见到了另一个上海，高楼大厦"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"和"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"精致"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"生活之外的"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"上海。"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"这里都是老旧的"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"居民区，街边的小店也是不怎么明亮，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"价格实惠，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"来吃饭的也大多是本地的"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"阿公阿婆"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"。在这里"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，我忽然有了一种"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"活的起的感觉，或者说，我是在生活的感觉。当然，这里毕竟是上海，随便"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"找个方向走上个三五里路，还是能看到繁华的商场，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"整洁的公园"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"。如果有心，穿过一些小巷子，还会发现藏在深处的别墅群和洋人区（"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"这一片好像是韩国人）（吐槽一下，上海"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"外国人居住的区域都很宽敞整洁"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"）。"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"这段时间里我是极少回去"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"市里的，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"少到我现在甚至回想不起来有什么相关的记忆。大概我本就"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"不喜欢繁华和热闹"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，也不是什么后"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"来才有的"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"心理。"}]},{"type":"text","level":0},{"type":"text","level":0,"children":[{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"那段日子回想起来是平和快乐的，工作不忙，中午可以回家睡一会，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"可以自己看一会书，下班后可以去河边散步，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"可以去健身，可以顺手买一份猪头肉。"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"可惜的是，公司过了半年多就"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"濒临倒闭"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"了，我无奈又开始了找工作之旅。也是在这次找工作"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"的"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"过程中，决定以三个"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"上海为题，写下这段内容。"}]},{"type":"text","level":0},{"type":"text","level":0,"children":[{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"１９的工作从上海找到了杭州，杭州呆了一年左右，在２０年"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"离职，再次回到上海。"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"这次我住到了宝山，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"一个更加偏僻的区。是的，那时候开始，我就真正意识到，我偏爱这种地方。"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"不要太时尚"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，不要太精致，街边有早餐，有"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"菜市场，有为生活"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"忙碌的人，这样就好。这次回到上海，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"宝山住了一年"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"左右，又跑到了曹路"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"。"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"之前虽然偏僻，但还算是市区，而这次"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，便已经到了城乡结合部"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"离家不远就有草莓地，再远"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"就"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"是"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"荒地了。偏僻但胜在价格便宜，３５００"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"／"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"月的两室一厅在上海已经是很低的价格了"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"我也"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"是工作后第一次"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"住上了整租的房子"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"。"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"八几年的老房子"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"条件自然是很差的，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"刚好满足了我自己装修的想法，于是那段时间里，我白天上班，晚上回家打"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"腻子，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"周末还要铺地板，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"花了些钱，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"出了"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"些力，费了些时间，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"终于房间也算是"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"像模像样了"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"只"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"可惜当时的照片找不到了"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"。"}]},{"type":"text","level":0},{"type":"text","level":0,"children":[{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"在这个房子住的时候，我还捡到一只猫，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"因为是七月底"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"捡到的，所以就叫她七妹了。"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"之后一次带她"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"去公园玩，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"她挣脱了牵绳跑掉了，去找了几次，也没找到，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"想来，现在她应该都做奶奶了。"}]},{"type":"text","level":0},{"type":"text","level":0,"children":[{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"在曹路住的日子也是我打工生涯最忙的日子"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"晚上加班，周末加班，甚至放假也有电话打过来，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"也是这段日子，让我决定告别打工生涯。回想曹路的样子，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"又是另一个上海"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"一个"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"生活的忙忙碌碌的"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"上海，一个充满了打工"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"气息的"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"上海，这里"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"大多是外地的打工人，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"街边的小店虽然便宜，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"但很少注重味道，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"不同于闵行的老旧但整洁，这里是老旧且凌乱"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，走上"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"几"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"里路，看到的也只是个"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"０"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"５年风格的老商场。在这里"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，临时居所的味道"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"远大于生活的味道。"}]},{"type":"text","level":0},{"type":"text","level":0,"children":[{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"原本三个上海，我想写的是"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"繁华的"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"市区－生活化的闵行－打工风的张江（"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"产生这个想法时候在的地方）。拖到今天"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"回看上海"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，发现"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"远不止这三面"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"市区"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"可以精致，可以时尚，可以生活化，也可以虚假"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"我很难完整的体验他们。"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"在此之外，上海还有更加偏僻的郊区"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"那里有"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"一年去"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"度假几次的人"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，有为了"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"落户而定居的"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"、"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"每天通勤"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"四"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"小时的人"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"，也有就在"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"那"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"里做生意的人。"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"我喜欢一个在这些地方闲逛，看看他们的生活，想象一下如果是自己"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"居住在此会是怎样。"},{"type":"text","level":0,"text":"只是有时候这么久了，会感到些清冷。"}]},{"type":"text","level":0},{"type":"text","level":0}]